flowchart TB
    subgraph sli[rg-sli-demo]
      FE[Frontend / Login] -. App Insights SDK .-> AI[Application Insights]
      BE[Backend / Checkout] -. App Insights SDK .-> AI
      AI --> LAW[(Log Analytics Workspace<br/>App Insights telemetry store)]
      AMW[(Azure Monitor Workspace<br/>SLI metrics)]
    end
    subgraph hm[rg-healthmodel-demo]
      MI[System-assigned identity]
      HM[Health model]
      HM --> ARG[Node: Azure Resource Graph]
      HM --> AIT[Node: App Insights topology]
      ARG --> E1[slidemo-fe / slidemo-be<br/>App Service entities]
      AIT --> E2[sli-demo-frontend / sli-demo-backend<br/>cloud-role components]
      E1 --> AL{{Health-state alerts<br/>Degraded / Unhealthy}}
      E2 --> AL
    end
    MI -->|Monitoring Reader + Data Reader| sli
    ARG -.->|Resource Graph query: App Services + plan| sli
    AIT -.->|reads App Insights topology| AI
    E1 ==>|AMW PromQL SLI signal| AMW
    E2 ==>|AMW PromQL SLI signal| AMW
    E2 -.->|recommended Log Analytics signal<br/>failed requests| LAW
